# 0.5.1

* Update verify template to expect 201 status rather than 200. 

# 0.5.0

* Strings within the package are now translatable using [angular-gettext](http://angular-gettext.rocketeer.be/).
* Added missing register template.

# 0.4.3

* Extend `scope.editUser` rather than overriding with
  a copy of the `$rootSope.user`.

# 0.4.2

* Register verify was using `reverseurl` rather then `reverseUrl`.

# 0.4.1

* Update `/register/verify/` route controller to new name.

# 0.4.0

* Allow for an optional deffered object to be passed in to directive methods.

# 0.3.0

* Handle errors on the profile form.

# 0.2.0

* Forms will no longer submit if they are pristine.
* All form directives now require a `name` attribute.

# 0.1.0

* Added option to `passwordChangeForm` directive to update rather than change
  the password.
* Added default placeholders, based on the label data, to all fields.
* Removed custom fields from registration and profile forms.

# 0.0.4

* Removed 'removeRedundantAttributes' options in htmlmin.

# 0.0.3

* Depends on angular 1.2.x rather than 1.2.7+.

# 0.0.2

* Use packaged version of angular-reverse-url.

# 0.0.1

* Pre-release version.
